en it from around her neck since I gave it to her. Her wedding gift to me was now in a box in Personal Effects, along with my money and everything else the Guard took off me when they locked me up. It was a charmed necklace that when activated would turn the wearer invisible. If only I had it now. I wish I WERE invisible.<br>
